definition: structural particle: used after a verb (or adjective as main verb), linking it to following phrase indicating effect, degree, possibility etc
to have to/must/ought to/to need to
to obtain/to get/to gain/to catch (a disease)/proper/suitable/proud/contented/to allow/to permit/ready/finished

to go out/to come out/to occur/to produce/to go beyond/to rise/to put forth/to happen/(used after a verb to indicate an outward direction or a positive result)/classifier for dramas, plays, operas etc

sentences.english: That's according to a new AP Ipsos poll.
sentences.chinese: 這是根據最新的美聯社依普索民意調查得出的結論。

sentences.english: If the conclusions can not be applied in practice, better dump them when it is still early.
sentences.chinese: 如果得出結論不能在實踐中應用，趁早扔了。

sentences.english: Therefore it is feasible to obtain the electronic administrative affairs of village in our country's new rural construction.
sentences.chinese: 由此得出電子村務在我國新農村建設中的可行性。

sentences.english: At last that RFID is IT Pioneer is concluded.
sentences.chinese: 最後本文得出RFID是IT“尖兵”的結論。

sentences.english: Still, like I used to tell you, no conclusions based on assumptions.
sentences.chinese: 還是如我所告訴你的，不能再假設中得出結論。

sentences.english: Although, only a human mind could invent something as insipid as love.
sentences.chinese: 儘管，只有人類思維才發明得出愛情這般乏味的東西。

sentences.english: Finally, he incorporated some compromises suggested by others into a specific motion.
sentences.chinese: 最後，他整合了一些各個方面建議，得出折衷議案。

sentences.english: This yields NT$18,000 or so of disposable income for each person in the household every month.
sentences.chinese: 得出家中每人每月可支配所得是一萬八千多元。

sentences.english: It's the best way out of this discussion.
sentences.chinese: 這是經過這次討論得出的最好做法。

sentences.english: These results suggest that the antimutagenic and anticancer effect of White Tea are better than that of Green Tea.
sentences.chinese: 由此得出，白茶的抗突變和體外抗癌效果好於綠茶。

sentences.english: I have arrived at seven billion myself, theoretically.
sentences.chinese: 在理論上，我自己得出的數字爲七十億。

sentences.english: The result obtained is of importance in guiding the ground-pressure control and mining procties.
sentences.chinese: 得出的結論對於控制地壓和採礦生產有指導意義。

sentences.english: Currid’s conclusion, based on dozens of interviews, is less sublime.
sentences.chinese: 克里德做了幾十個採訪後得出的結論可沒有這麼高尚。

sentences.english: The changes of the fabric characteristics can be qualitatively giv…
sentences.chinese: 通過分析可以定性地得出其特性的變化。

sentences.english: Moreover, the reactive force between slab and roller is obtained in this paper.
sentences.chinese: 此外，還得出了鑄坯對夾輥的作用力。

sentences.english: We both arrived at the same conclusion.
sentences.chinese: 我們兩個得出了一致的結論。
